description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 1: Biden says Cuomo should resign. New York Dems say Cuomo should go, but he's holding on. Only one New York governor has ever been impeached. Schumer says Cuomo should resign. Clay asks on Twitter: Will he go, not should he go? Biden's CDC unconstitutionally extends eviction moratorium. De Blasio defends vaccine passport that will kill NYC tourism.
